# Video files — never commit footage.
# Git keeps binaries in history forever, even after deletion. The spike clip is
# 68 MB of personal footage and is fully replaceable: drop any clip into
# spike/media/ and regenerate (see spike/README.md).
*.mp4
*.MP4
*.mov
*.MOV
*.m4v
*.mxf
*.braw

# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Expo / React Native (for when the app lands)
.expo/
dist/
web-build/
ios/Pods/
ios/build/
*.xcuserstate

# Env / secrets — Google OAuth client IDs live here
.env
.env.local
*.keystore

# macOS
.DS_Store
